title: For Sale:  Dillon Square Deal B Progressive Reloader
postcontent: For sale is my Dillon Precision SDB (Square Deal B) Progressive Reloader.  Setup for reloading 9x19mm (Luger).  This four-station reloader sizes an empty cartridge case, then de-primes the empty case.  From there it drops a powder charge that you adjust, slightly flairs the case mouth so you can seat the bullet which is then fully seated and crimped into position that won't work loose.  This reloading press is auto-indexing, which means that for every pull of the actuation handle each case moves to the next station and a completed round is produced and droped into a catch bin, ready to shoot.  The press should be mounted on a VERY SOLID bench of some sort so the press doesn't move or shake when the handle is pulled.  It is in perfect operating condition.  It comes with the powder and primers that are already loaded into the press as well as a zippered cover to keep it clean when not in use.Price is $200 firm.  No trades, please.  FTF transaction that is final, no shipping.
